{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_02_05",
  "title": "サニーピース 02 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "おかえりなさい\n久しぶりの実家はどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Welcome back.\nHow was your visit back home?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.1333334922,
      "endTime": 4.7023812293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま。帰省したのは久しぶりだけど\nあまりそんな感じはしなかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm back. It was my first time going back home in a while‚\nbut it didn't really feel that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9000001589,
      "endTime": 11.9762815158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "実家ってそういうものかもしれないわね\n久しぶりに帰っても、すぐに馴染んじゃうから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe that's how it is with family homes.\nEven if it's been a while‚ you quickly feel at home again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1666668255,
      "endTime": 18.7118369419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "それもあるけど、すずと芽衣がついて来たから\n二人が騒がしくて実家にいる気がしなかったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's part of it‚ but Suzu and Mei came with me‚\nand they were so noisy‚ it didn't feel like I was actually at home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9000001589,
      "endTime": 27.4367803255,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13599.999960200003,
          "startTime": 32.5000001191
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "あの二人はどこに行っても変わらないわね\n……そういえば、怜に手紙が届いてたわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Those two never change‚ wherever they go.\n…Speaking of which‚ you got a letter‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6333334922,
      "endTime": 33.9658280372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "私に手紙？\n差出人は……これ、お兄ちゃんからだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A letter for me?\nThe sender is… this is from my brother.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.1666668255,
      "endTime": 42.8108621914,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11133.333333399996,
          "startTime": 45.3000001589
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8833.333333399998,
          "startTime": 43.0000001589
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "封筒の中身は手紙と……ライブのチケット？\n……私に見に来てほしいって書いてある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a letter and… a live ticket inside?\n…He says he wants me to come see him.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.0000001589,
      "endTime": 53.479274717900005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "怜のお兄さんはバンドをやっているのよね？\nお兄さんも頑張っているのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your brother is in a band‚ right‚ Rei?\nHe's working hard too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.6666668255,
      "endTime": 58.795986779399996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、辛いことも沢山あったはずなのに\nずっとひたむきに頑張っているの。本当に尊敬するわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I'm sure he's been through a lot‚\nbut he's always kept going. I really respect him.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0000001589,
      "endTime": 67.9837865511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "それは怜も同じでしょ\nずっとアイドルを頑張ってるじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's the same for you‚ Rei.\nYou've been working hard as an idol too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.2000001589,
      "endTime": 72.5059179464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私はアイドルになりたかった訳じゃないから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I didn't become an idol because I wanted to…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.8000057537,
      "endTime": 78.0154706318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "（そう、私はみんなのように）\n（アイドルに憧れてアイドルになった訳じゃない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Yes‚ unlike everyone else‚)\n(I didn't become an idol because I admired them.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.3333370525,
      "endTime": 85.8405480701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "（昔の私はアイドルをただの手段だと思っていた）\n（そんな私に大切なことを気付かせてくれたのは……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I used to think of being an idol as just a means to an end.)\n(The person who made me realize what's important…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0333370525,
      "endTime": 95.9965116817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピースがデビューして間もない頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Shortly after Sunny Peace's debut.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0666703859,
      "endTime": 98.2000062624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 98.266672929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、またテンポが遅れてる！\n動きが雑になってるわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ your timing is off again!\nYour movements are sloppy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4333395957,
      "endTime": 104.43218307490001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "デビューライブが終わったからって気を抜かないで！\nもっと集中しなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't let your guard down just because the debut live is over!\nFocus!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.6333395957,
      "endTime": 109.7968091964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁはぁ……やっぱり怜ちゃんのレッスンは厳しいな\nでも、おかげでちゃんと上達してるって実感出来る……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant… Rei-chan's lessons are always so tough.\nBut I feel like I'm definitely improving thanks to them…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1333375612,
      "endTime": 122.7625211397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、レッスンに付き合ってくれてありがとう\n次のライブではもっとうまく踊れるように頑張るね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for practicing with me‚ Rei-chan.\nI'll work hard so I can dance better at the next live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0333365439,
      "endTime": 131.9666697501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は凄いわね。何度叱られても\n嫌な顔一つせずに毎日ハードなレッスンを続けて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ you're amazing. No matter how many times I scold you‚\nyou never complain and keep practicing hard every day…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.1999950725,
      "endTime": 141.076525529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、千紗はダンスが苦手なのに\nどうしてそこまで頑張れるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Chisa‚ you're not good at dancing‚\nso how can you work so hard?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.4333334921,
      "endTime": 148.15009107580002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "それは……アイドルになるのが夢だったから\n夢を叶えるためだから、辛くても頑張れるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's because… it was my dream to be an idol.\nI can work hard even when it's tough because I'm trying to achieve my dream.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.5333538371,
      "endTime": 157.5915850001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "……そうよね、千紗はアイドルが好きで\nアイドルになったんだものね。それに比べて私は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right‚ Chisa‚ you love idols‚\nand that's why you became one. Compared to that‚ I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.8666708944,
      "endTime": 167.7452193258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.0000032105,
      "endTime": 169.17746351140002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい\n私はみんなとは違うんだなぁって思っちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry.\nI just thought about how I'm different from everyone else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.3666698771,
      "endTime": 174.586012395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "デビューライブではみんな、アイドルが好きという\n気持ちが溢れて、眩しいくらい輝いていたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the debut live‚ everyone was overflowing with their love for idols‚\nthey were shining so brightly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.8000032105,
      "endTime": 181.9371008553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "そんなみんなを見ていると、引け目を感じるのよ\n私は好きでアイドルになった訳じゃないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel inferior when I see them like that.\nBecause I didn't become an idol because I loved it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.1333365438,
      "endTime": 190.1205246923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん……私達を見てそんな風に感じてたんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan… You felt that way when you looked at us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.3333365438,
      "endTime": 196.27778100939997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
