      "text": "（私にとってアイドルは親を納得させる手段でしかない）\n（自分のためにアイドルという立場を利用しているだけ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Being an idol is just a way for me to convince my parents.)\n(I'm just using my position as an idol for my own benefit.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.6999920206,
      "endTime": 205.77781546880001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
