      "text": "（そんな不純な動機でアイドルをしている私が）\n（純粋なみんなと一緒にいていいのかしら）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(With such impure motives‚ do I have the right)\n(to be with everyone‚ who is so pure?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.9666586873,
      "endTime": 213.1920780179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
