      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "少女",
      "speakerNameEn": "Girl",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "初めて見た時からずっと怜ちゃんのダンスが大好きです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've loved your dancing ever since I first saw you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 357.5999767618,
      "endTime": 362.19997676180003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "少女",
      "speakerNameEn": "Girl",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大ファンです。応援してます。頑張って下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm your biggest fan. I'm rooting for you! Keep up the good work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 362.1999767618,
      "endTime": 366.6777315454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 366.8666434285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei028.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう……凄く嬉しいわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you… I'm so happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 366.8666434285,
      "endTime": 370.78385429350004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei029.m4a",
      "text": "（ファンの応援ってこんなに嬉しいものなんだ）\n（こんなに勇気づけられるものなんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(To think that fans' support could be this heartwarming.)\n(That it could be so encouraging.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 371.06665767,
      "endTime": 378.2719182329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 378.46665767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei030.m4a",
      "text": "（私がテーマパークでキャストのダンスに憧れたように）\n（アイドルの私のダンスに憧れてくれる人がいる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Just like I was inspired by the cast members' dancing at the theme park‚)\n(there's someone who admires my dancing‚ now that I'm an idol.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 378.46665767,
      "endTime": 385.64729245470005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei031.m4a",
      "text": "（きっかけはなりゆきかもしれないけど）\n（私を見て喜んで、応援してくれる人がいるのなら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It might have all started by chance‚ but if there are people)\n(who are happy to see me‚ who are supporting me…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 385.8333243367,
      "endTime": 393.457269859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 393.66665767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei032.m4a",
      "text": "（私は本気でアイドルを頑張ってみたい）\n（みんなと一緒に、アイドルとして輝きたい！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I want to seriously give it my all as an idol.)\n(I want to shine brightly as an idol‚ with everyone!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 393.66665767,
      "endTime": 400.80863049789997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 401.9333243367
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "それで怜は、お兄さんのライブを見に行くの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you're going to see your brother's live‚ Rei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 403.0666719116,
      "endTime": 406.411637894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei033.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……私は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know… I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 406.6000052449,
      "endTime": 410.57363333669997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei034.m4a",
      "text": "（子供の頃、私はお兄ちゃんのギターが好きだった）\n（私がファン第一号だって言って）\n（お兄ちゃんを応援していた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(When I was little‚ I loved listening to my brother play the guitar.)\n(I told him I was his biggest fan‚)\n(and I supported him.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 411.0000093139,
      "endTime": 421.0666769106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei035.m4a",
      "text": "（お兄ちゃんも私の応援を励みに頑張ってきたのかしら）\n（ファンの応援に勇気づけられた、あの時の私みたいに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I wonder if he's been working hard because of my support.)\n(Just like I was encouraged by the fans' support back then.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 421.2921188034,
      "endTime": 432.07200581210003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei036.m4a",
      "text": "……お兄ちゃんのライブ、見に行くわ\n行って、お兄ちゃんを思いっきり応援してくる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'll go see my brother's live.\nI'll go cheer for him with all my heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 432.2723916687,
      "endTime": 439.5508495964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "そう。良かった\n……怜はアイドルになって少し変わったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good.\n…You've changed a bit since becoming an idol‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 439.7531852083,
      "endTime": 445.84332106880004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei037.m4a",
      "text": "そうかしら？　自分では分からないけど……\nでも、今とても楽しいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? I don't see it…\nBut I'm really enjoying myself now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 446.0531852083,
      "endTime": 453.9432983713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei038.m4a",
      "text": "父を認めさせたくて始めた仕事だけど、今は\nそんなことは関係なくアイドルを続けたいと思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It started as a way to get my father's approval‚ but now\nI want to keep being an idol‚ regardless of that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 454.1865409212,
      "endTime": 462.0512801485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_05-rei039.m4a",
      "text": "――だって私、アイドルが好きだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Because I like being an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 462.2532075879,
      "endTime": 465.8036157605,
